com.davidbracewell.io.structured

Class StructuredReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.davidbracewell.io.structured.StructuredReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CSVReader, JSONReader, XMLReader

    public abstract class StructuredReader
extends Object
implements Closeable
    Represents a class for reading data in a structured format, e.g. xml, json, yaml, etc. Individual implementations may provide extra functionality (e.g. read xml attributes).
    Author:
    David B. Bracewell
